categories: Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Qella'tak was a male Twi'lek Jedi Master of the Green Jedi during the Galactic War with the Sith Empire. Wielding two lightsabers in combat, he was one of the commanders of the Republic forces during the Battle of Corellia.

Master Qella'tak was first added to the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic as part of the Digital Expansion Star Wars: The Old Republic: Galactic Strongholds, which added Conquest Commanders to most of the dual-faction worlds. Qella'tak is a rare NPC enemy, and his place at the uptown tram station on Corellia is frequently occupied by a generic Veteran Jedi Battlemaster.
